---
---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#111111]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0] mb-4">Who It's For</h2>
    <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] text-lg mb-14 max-w-2xl">
      We work with operations-heavy businesses where manual overhead is quietly eating margin.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Construction -->
      <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0]">Construction Companies</h3>
        </div>

        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          You've got crews on three job sites, a project manager drowning in RFIs, and a superintendent who's manually entering time logs into software that crashes on Tuesdays. We've seen it. Here's what's actually eating your margin:
        </p>

        <!-- Who it serves -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">General Contractors</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">Subcontractors</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">Tool &amp; Equipment Rental</span>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Scheduling gaps.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Crew shows up, materials aren't there. Or materials are there, crew isn't. Both cost money.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">RFI delays.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> A question sits in someone's inbox for four days. The job stops. The clock runs.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Safety documentation.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Everyone knows it has to be done. Nobody wants to do the paperwork. Agents handle the capture, filing, and reminders.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Cost overruns.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Usually traceable to something that wasn't tracked in real time. Agents track it in real time.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/20 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">
          If you're running $2M+ in annual revenue and your admin overhead is still mostly manual, this is for you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Events & Rental -->
      <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-[#C9A84C]/20 transition-colors duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#C9A84C]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#C9A84C]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5m-9-6h.008v.008H12v-.008zM12 15h.008v.008H12V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H12v-.008zM9.75 15h.008v.008H9.75V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H9.75v-.008zM7.5 15h.008v.008H7.5V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008H7.5v-.008zm6.75-4.5h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008V15zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm2.25-4.5h.008v.008H16.5v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008H16.5V15z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#F0F0F0]">Event &amp; Rental Businesses</h3>
        </div>

        <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Party rental, catering, venues, and event planners. The logistics are brutal and the margins are thin. Your specific headaches:
        </p>

        <!-- Who it serves -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">Party Rental</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">Catering</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">Venues</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">Event Planners</span>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Inventory chaos.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> What's out? What's back? What's broken? Agents track all of it and flag conflicts before they become disasters.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Quoting takes forever.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Customer asks for a quote on Friday afternoon. It sits until Monday. They booked someone else. Agents can turn around quotes automatically based on availability and pricing rules.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Customer communication black holes.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Confirmation emails don't go out. Delivery windows don't get confirmed. Agents handle every touchpoint from booking to pickup.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#C9A84C] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#x25B8;</span>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[#F0F0F0] font-semibold">Logistics on event day.</span>
              <span class="text-[#9CA3AF]"> Routing, crew assignments, equipment manifests. The prep work that takes hours can be mostly automated.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-[#C9A84C] border border-[#C9A84C]/20 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 bg-[#C9A84C]/5">
          If your business runs on bookings and logistics, there's a lot of room to cut manual work here.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
